Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:10.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在逝去的時光中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.96,0:28:14.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}曾幾何時封閉了心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.19,0:28:17.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.39,0:28:20.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}向著呼喚聲的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.56,0:28:23.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}投向我的視線的目光
